text: Northampton Town F.C. is an English football club. They started in 1897 and are based in Northampton in the county of Northamptonshire. They play their home games at a stadium called Sixfields Stadium and are nicknamed "The Cobblers". ==League position== Season League Position 2000/01 Second Division 18th 2001/02 Second Division 20th 2002/03 Second Division 24th 2003/04 Third Division 6th 2004/05 League Two 7th 2005/06 League Two 2nd 2006/07 League One 14th 2007/08 League One 9th 2008/09 League One 21st ===Former position=== Category:English football clubs Category:Northampton Category:1897 establishments in the United Kingdom
